{"tid":1305431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強烈呼籲】咁多位地區遊行搞手入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-11T00:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T02:15:45.000Z","uid":191487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7c3d138a8073ff76cc76620b6cce8f97e65a68db","tid":1305431,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:33:06.000Z","msg":"首先好多謝各位有心同路人出黎開枝散葉，<br />\n地區運動係應該要搞落去，仲要長命做，將抗爭種子植入每區。<br />\n<br />\n只要訴求得宜，絕對可以將黃藍拉近，擴闊參與者光譜。但唔好忘記，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5大訴求先係主菜</span></span></strong>!!! 以後<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千奇咪再講7大訴求8大訴求</span></span></span></span></strong>，可以用類似既形式表達<br />\n<br />\n<ins>光復XX</ins><br />\n1. xxxxxxx (地區議題)<br />\n2. xxxxxxx (地區議題)<br />\n<br />\n<ins>五大訴求不退不撤</ins><br />\n1. 撤回法案<br />\n2. 釋放學生<br />\n3. 撤銷暴動定性<br />\n4. 追究警隊濫權<br />\n5. 解散立會，實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外現在見到兩個問題係，<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>1. 撞期</ins></strong><br />\n呢點好難避免，建議盡早係2-3星期前排期，或者係呢到專門出個遊行協調post，各搞手亦可以form 一個project grp，完左就散，以免成為大台。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2. 星期六日連搞兩場....</ins></strong><br />\n7.6 屯公<br />\n7.7 九龍<br />\n7.13 北區<br />\n7.14 沙田<br />\n7.27 紅土<br />\n7.28 將軍澳<br />\n<br />\n仲有蘊釀緊既西區，港島東.....<br />\n一個星期兩場，分薄左人數，又唔夠時間做文宣，參與者又攰，咁搞法8月未完18區都行哂，仲點做落去。<br />\n<br />\n咁多位，不如留番個星期六俾大家回氣啦好無，什至隔個星期先一場，相信效果會比較好。<br />\n<br />\n搭緊車打，sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"79c2da186829bd2af553342c6f18da1919ce1fbf","tid":1305431,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:48:51.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"39fedc7a460912c9370ae9e8d09fd7904f5122a1","tid":1305431,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:58:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"772aa2e3851e99fbf2aca5cd951a7d325e8bbee1","tid":1305431,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:04:36.000Z","msg":"pushhh"},{"pid":"7802e5f39d1c4725f36d4071a5aebbcb47e84eeb","tid":1305431,"uid":264493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:24:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7983a4a01b60076e10b85662a64c4f9f8bb7f5dc","tid":1305431,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:15:45.000Z","msg":"推"}]}